OL,3,CConstruction work begins on multi-
OL,4,Cmillion pound water sports facility
OL,6,FConstruction work begins today on a
OL,7,Fnew multi-million-pound water sports
OL,8,Ffacility in Dumfries and Galloway.
OL,10,FThe #6.7 million site will be built in
OL,11,FStranraer and is expected to open to
OL,12,Fthe public by the summer of 2026.
OL,14,FRepresentatives from the Stranraer
OL,15,FWater Sports Association - who are
OL,16,Fleading the project - and other
OL,17,Forganisations will attend a ceremony
OL,18,Ftoday to mark the beginning of
OL,19,Fconstruction work.
OL,21,FWhat is the project aiming to achieve?
